        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill establishes a statutory definition for <em>infrastructure</em>. The bill specifies that, except where context determines otherwise, the term <em>infrastructure</em> means bridges, dams, wharfs, roads, highways, ports, buildings, public utilities (including broadband), airports, and train stations.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
